    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Preserve the value, prestige and aesthetic of stainless steel sport or other luxury watches, while traveling stress and worry free, knowing your watch is safe, secure and free of damage. These completely clear watch travel cases or coffins ensure the safe transportation and storage of watches during travel, protecting them from moisture and dust, vibrations, potential scratches or damage to the inner mechanisms. A must have travel essentials item to keep time pieces safe, these watch coffins feature a double layer protection design; the transparent exterior plastic hard case has been designed to tightly fit the dense polystyrene material inner case. This thoughtful and lightweight design ensures no movement when you’re on the go, adding minimal weight to carry on bags or checked luggage</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux Clear Plastic Watch Case Coffin Travel Essentials Jewelry Organizers</h2>\n  <p>Preserve the value, prestige and aesthetic of stainless steel sport or other luxury watches, while traveling stress and worry free, knowing your watch is safe, secure and free of damage. These completely clear watch travel cases or coffins ensure the safe transportation and storage of watches during travel, protecting them from moisture and dust, vibrations, potential scratches or damage to the inner mechanisms.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>TRAVEL ESSENTIALS:</strong> A must have travel accessories item for luxury watches to keep time pieces safe, secure and free of moisture and dust, vibrations, potential scratches or damage to inner mechanisms</li>\n    <li><strong>LIGHTWEIGHT SECURE DESIGN:</strong> Double layer protection features clear plastic exterior watch box case and dense polystyrene material inner case to ensure no movement when travelling; lightweight construction adds minimal weight to carry on bags or checked luggage</li>\n    <li><strong>WATCH TRAVEL CASE:</strong> Compatible with most luxury stainless steel sport and other watches; watch coffin case is OEM industry standard used by luxury watch manufacturers worldwide, designed to provide additional security outside of standard product packaging</li>\n    <li><strong>EASY IDENTIFICATION:</strong> Entire watch travel case is clear on all sizes, allowing for the quick and easy identification of contents and quick retrieval when needed</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 4.75 x 2.5 x 2.5 inches; Single Case Weight: 0.20lbs; Material: Plastic Outer Case, Polystyrene Inserts</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/home/WC001_watch_travel_coffin_main.jpg\" alt=\"Preserve the value, prestige and aesthetic of stainless steel sport or other luxury watches, while traveling stress and worry free, knowing your watch\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 29229</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810131705060</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>A must have travel essentials item to keep time pieces safe, these watch coffins feature a double layer protection design; the transparent exterior plastic hard case has been designed to tightly fit the dense polystyrene material inner case. This thoughtful and lightweight design ensures no movement when you’re on the go, adding minimal weight to carry on bags or checked luggage. The clear watch box travel case allows for quick and easy identification of contents, as well as the quick retrieval of stainless steel sport watches when needed.</p>\n  <p>Compatible with most luxury stainless steel sport and other watches, the clear watch coffin travel case is OEM industry standard, used by luxury watch manufacturers worldwide, and has been designed to provide an added layer of security outside of standard product packaging for travel, storage or shipping. This watch box is durable and easy to open and close, providing a reliable solution for watch protection when traveling.</p>\n  <p>Dimensions: 4.75 (L) x 2.5 (W) x 2.5 (H) inches</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
